132	  it.todo("policy with two swords → insurance sum 2000 G, cap 4000 G");
133	  it.todo("two sword damages on a two-sword policy → each damage gets own deductible");
134	  it.todo("more damage entries than insured items of that type → rejected (throws)");
135	
